{"tid":1695361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"區議會文宣 建制議員支持何君堯","createTime":"2019-11-05T14:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T15:38:24.000Z","uid":51183,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3bd2bb97571b34eef50fdaeeee72e88e971b31","tid":1695361,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港議員何君堯，於7月21日元朗支持保鄉衛族村民<br />\n對抗黑衣暴徙表演出色，後被報復家墳亦受破壞<br />\n39名建制立法會議員聯署譴責，稱何為「敢言的議員」<br />\n而且何議員亦一向身體力行撐警，深受愛戴<br />\n區選在即，建制議員應該把握機會，支持何君堯<br />\n爭取五百萬沈默大多數選票<br />\n所以本人特意設計了一些概念文宣<br />\n免費供各建制議員參考<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n(注意：以下圖片為設計概念圖，並非競選廣告<br />\n未獲授權使用，本人不負上任何法律責任)</span><br />\n<br />\n示範圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/deE92jj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdeE92jj.jpg&h=cc948d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VV0Jnjk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVV0Jnjk.jpg&h=88342824&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b606d3cc3e41ca322b3fb11ac94667faba7a9213","tid":1695361,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1d685c87658b08bce8a7ac428b870200250dab","tid":1695361,"uid":51183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"做多咗空白/部份建制派議員<br />\n咁就貼埋上來<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位千祈唔好自己P參選緊既建制區議員上去<br />\n同埋千祈唔好周街貼呀 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VSxonm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSxonm7.jpg&h=3257f2ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zzLJnm7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzzLJnm7.jpg&h=01c974ea&s={